{"tid":150183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有J圖】台中公園「做愛女」：「先生要做愛嗎？一百塊。」","createTime":"2017-03-09T23:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T13:43:53.000Z","uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20004b8c2de78ae64c463c55abd3bce713c0b4c2","tid":150183,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T23:46:20.000Z","msg":"「先生來做愛吧，一百塊！」一位民眾星期一下午近2點直擊，在台中公園的日月湖旁花圃一名年約40歲的女子，看見他走近，就在2公尺外的距離開口詢問：「先生要做愛嗎？一百塊。」讓他連忙揮手拒絕。新聞曝光後，《蘋果》重回現場發現該名女子在同一個地點，同樣跟遊客搭訕，警方或是社會局人員完全神隱，網友質疑：「萬一遇到壞人怎麼辦？」<br />\n腦中滿是疑問的民眾逛完公園準備回家，該名女子還在花圃旁，看見他走過居然還是上前詢問：「先生來作愛吧，一百塊，三個小時。」<br />\n台中第二警分局台中公園駐在所警員說，並未接獲相關訊息，「且過程並不合理」，查證後發現，近期有一名精神異常女子經常在公園出沒，該女已經有2次強制送醫紀錄，將調閱監視器確認是否是同一人。<br />\n <br />\n新聞曝光後，不少網友感覺心酸，《蘋果》9日上午重回台中公園，該名女子竟然就在同一個位置、用同樣方式跟遊客攀談，即使記者已經詢問轄區警方，該名女子依然在派出所後方騷擾民眾，連外籍勞工都不放過，一個鐘頭內完全不見警員或是社工出現，民眾痛批：「市長出國就沒有人做事情了嗎？」（王乙徹／台中報導）<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C88Oix8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC88Oix8.jpg&h=5228f3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/074536_7ce1a637d5ce721a3e89166dde5a345d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F074536_7ce1a637d5ce721a3e89166dde5a345d.jpg&h=54595e63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/074536_dbe1483f732596b4ae80707f5a65fe25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F074536_dbe1483f732596b4ae80707f5a65fe25.jpg&h=870916a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20170309/1072312/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flocal%2F20170309%2F1072312%2F&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=db9116f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20170309/1072312/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b3efc9ecf2b34638f19255de90a20bbbed718e","tid":150183,"uid":70561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T23:49:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24bf5de6c3782bcc019893e00440e8b0c62e836c","tid":150183,"uid":19660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T23:50:22.000Z","msg":"阿凡達熱潮過晒啦喎"},{"pid":"fc743c6f429fe67e81205e2a19f28f89a6f3c0c1","tid":150183,"uid":16689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T23:54:12.000Z","msg":"一百蚊基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa06654a6027e41c25aebd84e885e075cb36ea1","tid":150183,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T00:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿凡達熱潮過晒啦喎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc1b088d51da581b7ce4dc9d00e891863d93350","tid":150183,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T00:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edeacd4fbf9998ca5b7f7afa610738e5886acc07","tid":150183,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T01:17:30.000Z","msg":"一百蚊，三小時<br />\n時薪仲低過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409313a7591b15050c0fdabfe40d612445470136","tid":150183,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T01:19:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>阿凡達熱潮過晒啦喎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd38f2687484be6412615b1593632651f2770441","tid":150183,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T01:21:12.000